    public static class MetadataTemplate.FieldOperation
extends BoxJSONObject
    Posssible operations that can be performed in a Metadata template.
    • Add an enum option
    • Edit an enum option
    • Remove an enum option
    • Add a field
    • Edit a field
    • Remove a field
    • Edit template
    • Reorder the enum option
    • Reorder the field list
